&lt;h2 id=&quot;show-notes&quot;&gt;Show Notes&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The folks at the Stop, Hack, and Roll podcast have announced a New Year, New Game, Game Jam. In this episode, Andrew Cedotal, Dustin Freeman, and I discuss our ideas for submissions to the game jam.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I ended up changing the setting of my game to dystopic underground bunker. The final version I submitted to the jam is &lt;a href=&quot;https://diegeticgames.com/game_files/Loyalty-Celebration.pdf&quot;&gt;Loyalty Celebration&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also, I’ve launched a &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.patreon.com/randylubin&quot;&gt;Patreon&lt;/a&gt; for my game designs: &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.patreon.com/randylubin&quot;&gt;https://www.patreon.com/randylubin&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

